#Approach:

=========================================
ZERO SUM SUBARRAY
(Prefix Sum + HashMap)
=========================================

🔹 Idea

Prefix Sum use karo.

Agar same prefix sum dobara mil jaye,
to beech ka subarray ka sum = 0 hoga.

Reason:

PrefixSum(j) - PrefixSum(i) = 0

⇒ PrefixSum(j) = PrefixSum(i)

-----------------------------------------

🔹 Key Observation

Zero Sum Subarray exist karta hai if:

1. Prefix Sum = 0
   (Starting se current index tak sum 0)

OR

2. Same Prefix Sum repeat ho jaye
   (Beech ka portion 0 ban jayega)

-----------------------------------------

🔹 Approach

1. Running Prefix Sum maintain karo.
2. Har index par sum update karo.
3. Agar sum == 0
      return true
4. Agar same sum pehle bhi aa chuka hai
      return true
5. Warna sum HashMap me store kar do.
6. End tak kuch na mile
      return false

-----------------------------------------

